{
  "3234100": {
    "name": "丧尸要塞：末日搜打撤",
    "steam_appid": 3234100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/e4eac81f1d25f0bafbd7c28f30419cca.avif?t=1770464129\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《丧尸要塞：末日搜打撤》中，冲进被感染的城市废墟，翻箱倒柜搜刮补给、砸烂丧尸的脑袋、在撤离点浴血突围！二十分钟持续燃烧肾上腺素——是继续贪战搜刮，还是丢下战利品拼命撤离。枪声、尖叫与倒计时交织成一场生存极限的狂欢，带着物资成功脱身都像从地狱归来般酣畅淋漓，至于怎么地狱的你先别问！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/5f012405685af574333dd85bb2897269.poster.avif?t=1770464129\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/5f012405685af574333dd85bb2897269.webm?t=1770464129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/777eeae72b20243ee751eebdf9adb3d4.avif?t=1770464129\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别再低估它们！《丧尸要塞：末日搜打撤》的这些丧尸拥有高度智能——它们会思考、会协作、会包抄。借助独特的路径算法，它们能绕过障碍、共享情报、合围玩家。被发现的瞬间，它们会咆哮并召唤同类，形成可怕的狩猎群！你的开枪与移动，都会改变它们的策略，一旦暴露位置，逃亡将成为唯一的生机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/2a7629f0e9fe6ac01fb022283c33529a.poster.avif?t=1770464129\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/2a7629f0e9fe6ac01fb022283c33529a.webm?t=1770464129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>营地管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >营地是一个需要持续管理的动态系统。当幸福度、卫生、住所和资源之间的平衡被打破时，营地秩序会迅速崩溃。保持营火燃烧，清理垃圾和排泄物，建造住所，并保持营地居民的士气。你做出的每一个决定都会直接塑造营地的未来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/e1ecdbebce336bc07efd90824eef450f.avif?t=1770464129\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《丧尸要塞：末日搜打撤》的手绘像素风的废土城市中，陷阱与物资同样遍布。拉响陷阱、摆好炮台、引爆油桶——用环境碾碎追击你的丧尸群，化被动为主动！背包内旋转、拼凑、挪动——每一次完美塞入都能让人爽到起鸡皮疙瘩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/81f65882c5ce14cef0bfe6d50bdb9db0.poster.avif?t=1770464129\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/81f65882c5ce14cef0bfe6d50bdb9db0.webm?t=1770464129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/c5c8b9861cab2ede0481b7ee578092fe.avif?t=1770464129\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《丧尸要塞：末日搜打撤》的战火与腐朽之间，仍有幸存者在废墟中苟延残喘。——有人交易，有人撒谎，也有人只想讲完最后一个故事。你可以选择帮他们一程，也可以利用他们。每一次交谈都像踩在细线之上，善意或贪念，只差一念之间。即使世界崩塌，篝火旁那点微弱的光，依然让人不舍得离开！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/59aefe833ff0a3b58907b638ff54ed7a.poster.avif?t=1770464129\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/59aefe833ff0a3b58907b638ff54ed7a.webm?t=1770464129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧张刺激的10-20分钟生存任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有动态群体行为的先进丧尸AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工制作的像素艺术环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配备战略陷阱和防御炮台的动态环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品管理系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可合成物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有特殊类型的可扩展背包系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基地建设与交易系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的幸存者故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4位独特的可选角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike进程系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/90c14edb4e1691a6b4a9e4ee80d38154.poster.avif?t=1770464129\" width=800 height=533 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234100/extras/90c14edb4e1691a6b4a9e4ee80d38154.webm?t=1770464129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
